summary: THE DRIVER SIDE REAR DOOR LATCH STOPPED WORKING.  THE DOOR WILL NO LONGER REMAIN CLOSED.  I GOT INTO THE VEHICLE AND STARTED IT UP AND NOTICED THE WARNING LIGHT ABOUT THE DOOR BEING AJAR.  I TRIED TO CLOSE IT BUT IT WOULD NOT LATCH AND THE WARNING WOULD NOT TURN OFF.  I HAD TO TIE THE DOOR SHUT SO I COULD DRIVE THE VEHICLE HOME.
